name: Well-earned Command (V)
Lore: 'Imperial officers often simulate large-scale battles with hologram games to improve their tactical ability. Those who excel at these games often mark themselves for advancement.',
Text: 'Deploy on a battleground site. At sites where you have a vehicle with armor and an Imperial general (or Imperial commander), your total battle destiny is +3 and opponent may not draw more than two battle destiny. If opponent controls this site, this Effect lost.',
